
Since Version 0.10.0... for older version, see README

What tou need :
   cmake - minimum version 2.6.0
   fftw - optional

If you want to change the default install directory :
   Edit CMakeLists.txt in the root directory of FlowDesigner and change the path...
   Default (in order : Windows, Mac, Linux):
      IF(WIN32)
         SET(CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX "C:/Progra~1/FlowDesigner")
      ELSE(WIN32)
         IF(APPLE)
            SET(CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX "/usr/local")
         ELSE(APPLE)
            SET(CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX "/usr")
         ENDIF(APPLE)
     ENDIF(WIN32)

To compile :
   % cd <path to the root of FlowDesigner>
   % cmake .
   % make
   % make install
